@startuml sequence_auth
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #0F3A6E
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBackgroundColor #EEF5FF
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #0F3A6E
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #EEF5FF
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #0F3A6E
skinparam sequenceNoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam sequenceNoteBorderColor #F9A825

title Authentification Enseignant / Admin et filtrage RLS

actor "Enseignant\n/ Admin" as U
participant "Application\n(React)" as App
participant "Supabase Auth\n(GoTrue)" as Auth
database "PostgreSQL\n(RLS activé)" as DB

== Authentification ==
U -> App : Saisit email + mot de passe
App -> Auth : supabase.auth.signInWithPassword()\n{ email, password }
Auth -> Auth : Vérification des identifiants\n+ génération JWT
Auth --> App : Session JWT\n(sub: uid, app_metadata: {is_admin})

note right of Auth
  Le JWT contient :
  • auth.uid() : UUID de l'utilisateur
  • is_admin (app_metadata)
  • expiry / refresh token
end note

== Accès aux données protégées (RLS) ==
App -> DB : SELECT * FROM classes\n[Authorization: Bearer JWT]
DB -> DB : Décode le JWT\n→ auth.uid() = "abc-123"
DB -> DB : Évalue la politique RLS :\nUSING (teacher_id = auth.uid())
DB --> App : Lignes dont teacher_id = "abc-123"
App --> U : Affiche uniquement\nSES classes

== Accès Admin (SECURITY DEFINER) ==
App -> DB : SELECT * FROM admin_list_users()
DB -> DB : Vérifie raw_app_meta_data->>'is_admin'
alt is_admin = true
  DB --> App : Liste de tous les enseignants
else is_admin = false
  DB --> App : RAISE EXCEPTION\n'Access denied: admin only'
end

@enduml
